---
// How It Works section - process explanation (US-004)
---

<section data-test="how-it-works" id="how-it-works" class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          The RootSpec Process
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Four simple skills that turn messy ideas into bulletproof specifications.
          Each step builds on the last, creating an unbreakable chain from vision to working code.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Skills Grid -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-16">
        <!-- rs-init -->
        <div data-test="skill-rs-init" class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 100 4m0-4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 100 4m0-4v2m0-6V4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">/rs-init</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
            Set up your project with the RootSpec framework. Creates the structure and tools you need.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- rs-spec -->
        <div data-test="skill-rs-spec" class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">/rs-spec</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
            Transform your idea into a structured 5-level specification with built-in validation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- rs-impl -->
        <div data-test="skill-rs-impl" class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">/rs-impl</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
            Generate working code from your specification. Test-driven, autonomous implementation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- rs-validate -->
        <div data-test="skill-rs-validate" class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-900 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">/rs-validate</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
            Run comprehensive tests to ensure your implementation matches the specification.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Workflow Visualization -->
      <div data-test="workflow-visual" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-50 to-blue-50 dark:from-gray-800 dark:to-blue-900/30 rounded-2xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8">
          From Idea to Working Application
        </h3>

        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <!-- Before State -->
          <div data-test="before-state" class="space-y-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 mb-4">
              📝 Before: Traditional Approach
            </h4>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 border border-red-200 dark:border-red-800 rounded-lg p-4">
                <p class="text-sm text-red-800 dark:text-red-300">
                  "Build a user-friendly dashboard with good UX"
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 border border-red-200 dark:border-red-800 rounded-lg p-4">
                <p class="text-sm text-red-800 dark:text-red-300">
                  "Make it scalable and maintainable"
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 border border-red-200 dark:border-red-800 rounded-lg p-4">
                <p class="text-sm text-red-800 dark:text-red-300">
                  "Ensure high performance and accessibility"
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 italic">
              Result: Endless debates, missed requirements, spec drift
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- After State -->
          <div data-test="after-state" class="space-y-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 mb-4">
              ✨ After: RootSpec Approach
            </h4>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 border border-green-200 dark:border-green-800 rounded-lg p-4">
                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-green-800 dark:text-green-300">
                  L1: Philosophy → Clear mission and values
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 border border-green-200 dark:border-green-800 rounded-lg p-4">
                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-green-800 dark:text-green-300">
                  L2: Truths → Measurable principles
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 border border-green-200 dark:border-green-800 rounded-lg p-4">
                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-green-800 dark:text-green-300">
                  L3: Interactions → Specific user flows
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 border border-green-200 dark:border-green-800 rounded-lg p-4">
                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-green-800 dark:text-green-300">
                  L4: Systems → Concrete architecture
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 border border-green-200 dark:border-green-800 rounded-lg p-4">
                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-green-800 dark:text-green-300">
                  L5: Implementation → Testable stories
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 italic">
              Result: Unambiguous requirements, automated testing, zero drift
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>